{"tid":1702310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人嘅革命幾時先可以唔好停留喺報仇嘅階段？","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T09:42:31.000Z","uid":77393,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"43d88f74f5bab51617dce66dd810a060574a1e8a","tid":1702310,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"係 無數位義士嘅仇一定要報<br />\n<br />\n但調返轉諗點解我哋一定要俾政府黑警無理壓榨/有手足出事先識得'口號上'進化<br />\n<br />\n第一次 加油 就送中條例<br />\n第二次 反抗 就蒙面惡法<br />\n第三次 報仇 就周義士嘅犧牲<br />\n<br />\n難聽講句 每次出事先換嚟香港人團結 但維持冇耐又互相開始分化 咁樣真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 如果想贏呢場革命<br />\n就要記得<br />\n我哋係為民主自由而抗爭<br />\n只要一日未爭取到真普選/獨立<br />\n就一日都唔可以放棄<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11.10 7區開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n11.11 全港三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b73636dd8ac5a8f003773e96a9f15da68e2e444f","tid":1702310,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"ff80fe24ef8ba9ddfe9033e33f1f1496e7c9fc84","tid":1702310,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"4a0f0016794fbca1b75c3b71a3846901acb00401","tid":1702310,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"74ac03d9378de37bfbbd3f670b8cb627be1f74c2","tid":1702310,"uid":51814,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"暴力，一直都係由執法者帶起。發覺近來藍屍都主力抹黑手足嘅「反抗行動」，我話係「反抗行動」係基於而家所有嘅行為(果)，都係對6.12防暴警用過度暴力(因)嘅回應。"},{"pid":"b9fcb5330215ffda0731aea4e1523231f430c685","tid":1702310,"uid":44180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,