.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecaa031e26a9ce9c523c4b6219e89205e94a2c23","tid":1702310,"uid":71564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"香港人 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d158294fb2740b86a13bfb02bd5606613534c39a","tid":1702310,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:58:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8bf55045ed258ef41f62ef280d683abe2fd2bf7","tid":1702310,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecaa031e26a9ce9c523c4b6219e89205e94a2c23","tid":1702310,"uid":71564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"香港人 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:18:28.000Z","msg":"呢個口號最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a90f844f9358b4708bbd3713e169bd78c378641","tid":1702310,"uid":188058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d88f74f5bab51617dce66dd810a060574a1e8a","tid":1702310,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"係 無數位義士嘅仇一定要報<br />\n<br />\n但調返轉諗點解我哋一定要俾政府黑警無理壓榨/有手足出事先識得'口號上'進化<br />\n<br />\n第一次 加油 就送中條例<br />\n第二次 反抗 就蒙面惡法<br />\n第三次 報仇 就周義士嘅犧牲<br />\n<br />\n難聽講句 每次出事先換嚟香港人團結 但維持冇耐又互相開始分化 咁樣真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 如果想贏呢場革命<br />\n就要記得<br />\n我哋係為民主自由而抗爭<br />\n只要一日未爭取到真普選/獨立<br />\n就一日都唔可以放棄<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11.10 7區開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n11.11 全港三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"尋日FA講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真報仇唔應該係我地既動力<br />\n呢樣正正呼應番樓主同FA講既有事發生大家先會因為憤怒先行動, 先團結<br />\n有問題既係制度/政府 而唔係純粹一件事/一班人<br />\n唔好因為發生令人憤慨既事而出黎 要因為制度不公而出黎<br />\n咁樣心態上先可以持久"},{"pid":"2d5b01ac6da3e7cf86c15245fe0bf00e9ce7ed33","tid":1702310,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"895154e59f375cec21637a6d6553d671114dc42d","tid":1702310,"uid":83914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e000f8c428f82f8b7fb4de2ec9b9bc26f5d0f6f","tid":1702310,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:02:34.000Z","msg":"我寧願發生左事點都有返啲變化好過無<br />\n無話齋口號變左都係咁話<br />\n101健仔中完槍之後都好似無乜回響咁都頹左一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw到底有無人知健仔咩情況架其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:04:59.000Z","msg":"最大轉變我反而覺得係蒙面法後O既星期二...一大班休息撚出黎吹風...跟著就頹到依家....係頹到依家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"明明當晚士氣大好<br />\n但之後就突然頹到依家"},{"pid":"f5c190ca0be1bfdd882abf790d5858062160a1aa","tid":1702310,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:48:08.000Z","msg":"聽口號都知啦大佬。報仇係其中一個口號，由加油進化到反抗再進化到報仇，可以知大家對呢個政府既憤怒有憎無減。唔好唔記得仲有五大訴求 缺一不可， 光復香港 時間革命呢d.<br />\n雖然香港人都係得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180634cdf496359a71fe0a905f0fb8d053fb741e","tid":1702310,"uid":126138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借借位+幫你推post<br />\n<br />\n【外國戰線】痴撚線，德國巴絲又發功（漢堡電影會＋嘉賓訪談）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702807</a>"},{"pid":"89b99302b51d9ac68f5e9a4bf027f755caf09164","tid":1702310,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"罷工"}]}